<node id="&quot;THORACIC OUTLET SYNDROME&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Thoracic Outlet Syndrome (TOS) is a condition where the blood vessels or nerves between the collarbone and first rib are compressed, causing symptoms such as arm pain and tingling."</data>
