</node>
<node id="&quot;SIGNIFICANT INCREASE IN SOFT TISSUE DENSITY IN THE LEFT UPPER LOBE WITH INVASION INTO THE MEDIASTINAL FAT AND NUMEROUS NEW OR ENLARGED CENTRAL NODES CONCERNING FOR PROGRESSION OF MALIGNANCY. ADDITIONALLY A PARENCHYMAL RIGHT MIDDLE LOBE NODULE IS INCREASED SINCE. THE MASS ENCASES THE LEFT PULMONARY VASCULATURE AND THE BRONCHI, SOME OF WHICH ARE NARROWED OR OCCLUDED. CONSOLIDATION IN THE LEFT UPPER AND LEFT LOWER LOBES MAY BE RESULT OF POST-OBSTRUCTIVE PNEUMONIA IN THE SETTING OF THE INCREASED SOFT TISSUE MASS. THE MASS IS IN CLOSE CONTACT WITH THE PERICARDIUM, AND PERICARDIAL INVOLVEMENT CANNOT BE EXCLUDED. SMALL-MODERATE LEFT PLEURAL EFFUSION.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"This is an event describing multiple significant findings from the CT scan, including potential progression of malignancy, post-obstructive pneumonia, and other related conditions."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-252c57b86f973f9f81c0df7c2db6350f</data>
</node>
